data.title: Steve Madden Music Presents: TAY JARDINE
data.description:
Steve Madden Music Presents: Tay Jardine - The adorable, witty & talented frontwoman from We Are the In Crowd made a great addition to Steve Madden Music with her infectious personality and cute sense of style. 

This is the behind-the-scenes exclusive footage with Tay Jardine from her photo shoot with Steve Madden Music.
